Adult male.description: Kentucky Warblers are smaller than Yellow-breasted Chats with a smaller bill, shorter tail and a completely yellow belly.

Female.description: Kentucky Warblers are smaller than Yellow-breasted Chats. Female Kentucky Warblers also have a smaller bill, shorter tail and a completely yellow belly unlike Yellow-breasted Chats.

Adult.description: Yellow-throated Vireos are smaller than Yellow-breasted Chats with a yellow-olive (not brownish gray) head and 2 white wingbars.

Adult male.description: Common Yellowthroats are smaller than Yellow-breasted Chats with a black mask instead of white spectacles seen on Yellow-breasted Chats.

Female.description: Common Yellowthroats are smaller than Yellow-breasted Chats. Females have yellow (not white) undertail coverts.
